internet, streaming video, gaming, dan tugas komputasi sehari-hari lainnya.</p>', '', 'de8cab40-ca41-4609-83a6-b9194dacb730', '2023-11-17', 'Baru', 20000000, 1, '', '/public/uploads/aset/tetap/wehhTgwVwuMhI5Qrv98FsHdD04Rc3G.jpg', 'wehhTgwVwuMhI5Qrv98FsHdD04Rc3G.jpg', 'Unit', '2024-07-29 06:30:32', '2024-08-18 04:20:12'),
